#ifndef IMAGEPLUS_CORE_HPP
#define IMAGEPLUS_CORE_HPP

//!
//! \namespace imageplus
//!
//! \brief core module for ImagePlus library
//!
//! This is the core module of the ImagePlus library. This module contains the basic functionality
//! of the library:
//!   - Basic config and types [imageplus_types.hpp, config.hpp]
//!   - multiarray and imavol class:
//!      - Definitions [multiarray.hpp, imavol.hpp]
//!      - Operations [multiarray_arithmetic.hpp, imavol_arithmetic.hpp, imavol_logical.hpp]
//!      - Comparisons [multiarray_comparison.hpp, imavol_comparison.hpp]
//!      - Debug output [multiarray_iostream.hpp]
//!      - copy and paste of specific parts [rectangles.hpp]
//!   - image and volume classes
//!      - Image definitions [image.hpp, imagegray.hpp, imagergb.hpp, imageyuv.hpp, imageyuv420.hpp, imageyuv422.hpp, imagemask.hpp, imagepartition.hpp]
//!      - Volume definitions [volume.hpp, volumegray.hpp, volumergb.hpp, volumeyuv.hpp]
//!   - Conversion operations:
//!      - Between data types [convert_types.hpp]
//!      - Between colorspace [convert_colorspace.hpp]
//!      - Between packed arrays and planar imageplus classes [convert_packed.hpp]
//!   - Exceptions for errors [exceptions.hpp]
//!   - Point and coordinates classes [point.hpp, point2d.hpp, point3d.hpp, point_geometry.hpp, coord.hpp, coord2d.hpp, coord3d.hpp, coord_logical.hpp]
//!   - Bounding box classes and operations [bbox.hpp,bbox2d.hpp,bbox3d.hpp]
//!   - Adding / removing borders [border.hpp]
//!   - camera and room classes [camera.hpp,room.hpp]
//!   - Basic filters:
//!      - class definition [filter.hpp, filterempty.hpp]
//!      - clipping operations [clipping.hpp]
//!      - thresholding [threshold.hpp]
//!
